{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三章讲述了萧秋水在桂湖遭遇三才剑客（笛剑江秀音、琴剑温艳阳、胡剑登雕梁）的伏击。三人才剑客以音乐为诱饵，用三才剑法合击萧秋水，萧秋水渐落下风。危急时刻，邓玉函、左丘超然和唐方及时赶到救援。邓玉函击败江秀音，左丘超然制服温艳阳，唐方以飞刀重伤登雕梁。萧秋水感念三才剑客的知音之情，劝说他们弃暗投明。三才剑客最终离去，萧秋水与兄弟们重聚。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_diao_liang",
      "speaker_name": "登雕梁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台既然身逢大难，又有缘得此相见，蒙兄赏听，吾辈当再奏一首，以解兄台内心积郁。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怕。我最怕就是死。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiu_yin",
      "speaker_name": "江秀音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何你现在不怕？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiu_yin",
      "speaker_name": "江秀音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要是我们觉得你怕，就不杀你呢？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我萧某人要生要死，不须要别人来决定！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在也是。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "温艳阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怨我们？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "温艳阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是被我们用计而擒，现在只要我手上一送，你就——",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "温艳阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜，可惜我身上还有任务未了……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "温艳阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我们还是骗了你，",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "温艳阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为……因为……因为我们就是三绝神剑的三名同门，笛剑江秀音，琴剑温艳阳，胡剑登雕梁。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们……你们就是‘三才剑客’！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "温艳阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三剑联手，江湖莫敌！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_diao_liang",
      "speaker_name": "登雕梁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拔你的剑。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_diao_liang",
      "speaker_name": "登雕梁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好剑！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是权力帮中的？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_diao_liang",
      "speaker_name": "登雕梁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。我们自小无父无母，加入了三绝剑派一门，所以掌门要我们做什么，便得做什么。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闻三位琴音笛韵，当非匪患之辈，难道孔扬秦所作所为，不是权力帮傀儡？！难道权力帮向来所作所为，三位充耳不闻？！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_diao_liang",
      "speaker_name": "登雕梁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知你心中不服，但二十二年前，若无孔掌门人，我们又岂有今日？身不由己啊，身不由己！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_diao_liang",
      "speaker_name": "登雕梁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "得罪！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是邓玉平，是邓玉函。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要不死，自然都来了。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这三人，杀还是不杀？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然不杀。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何不杀？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像……好像是因为……因为刚才他们也没有杀我……不，不不不不，我太高兴了，高兴得连话都不知该怎么说，连理由都不知道了……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你真的放了他？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说不杀，我就不杀。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_diao_liang",
      "speaker_name": "登雕梁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐姑娘，你这一刀我也许接得下，但登某也知接不下你下一刀。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yan_yang",
      "speaker_name": "温艳阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以一对一，我非你之敌。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 13
    }
  ],
